Path: md-docs/billing-system.md
 1	# Billing System
 2	
 3	## Overview
 4	The Billing System in SkyPANEL manages all financial transactions, subscriptions, and invoicing for the platform. It integrates with payment gateways, tracks usage, and handles billing cycles for both customers and administrators.
 5	
 6	## Table of Contents
 7	- [Features](#features)
 8	- [Architecture](#architecture)
 9	- [Pricing Models](#pricing-models)
 10	- [Payment Gateways](#payment-gateways)
 11	- [Subscription Management](#subscription-management)
 12	- [Invoicing](#invoicing)
 13	- [Usage Tracking](#usage-tracking)
 14	- [Tax Handling](#tax-handling)
 15	- [Reporting](#reporting)
 16	- [Security](#security)
 17	- [Error Handling](#error-handling)
 18	- [Configuration](#configuration)
 19	
 20	## Features
...
 33	
 34	### Components
 35	- **BillingService**: Core billing logic
 36	- **PaymentProcessor**: Handles payment gateway integration
 37	- **InvoiceGenerator**: Creates and manages invoices
 38	- **UsageTracker**: Tracks resource usage for billing
 39	- **TaxCalculator**: Handles tax calculations
 40	- **NotificationService**: Sends billing-related notifications
 41	
 42	### Data Flow
 43	1. Subscription created/updated
 44	2. Usage data collected
 45	3. Billing cycle ends
 46	4. Invoice generated
 47	5. Payment processed
 48	6. Receipt sent
 49	7. Records updated
 50	
 51	## Pricing Models
 52	
 53	### Subscription Plans
 54	1. **Fixed Price**
 55	 - Monthly/Annual billing
 56	 - Feature-based tiers
 57	 - Flat rate per period
 58	
 59	2. **Usage-Based**
 60	 - Pay-per-use pricing
 61	 - Tiered pricing
 62	 - Overage charges
...
