 17	
 18	## Overview
 19	
 20	SkyPANEL integrates with VirtFusion to provide comprehensive VPS hosting management capabilities. This integration allows users to manage their virtual servers, monitor resources, and handle billing through a unified interface.
 21	
 22	## Prerequisites
 23	
 24	- VirtFusion API access
 25	- Valid API credentials
 26	- Sufficient permissions for the required operations
 27	- Network access to the VirtFusion API endpoint
 28	
 29	## Setup and Configuration
 30	
 31	### Environment Variables
 32	
 33	Add the following environment variables to your `.env` file:
 34	
 35	```env
 36	# VirtFusion Configuration
 37	VIRT_FUSION_API_URL=https://api.virtfusion.example.com
 38	VIRT_FUSION_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
 39	VIRT_FUSION_API_SECRET=your_api_secret_here
 40	VIRT_FUSION_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your_webhook_secret
 41	```
 42	
 43	### Initialization
...
 63	
 64	export const virtFusionService = new VirtFusionService();
 65	```
 66	
 67	## API Integration
 68	
 69	### Authentication
 70	
 71	SkyPANEL uses API key authentication to communicate with the VirtFusion API. The authentication is handled automatically by the `VirtFusionAPI` class.
 72	
 73	### Rate Limiting
 74	
 75	The integration includes built-in rate limiting to prevent hitting VirtFusion API limits:
 76	
 77	- 60 requests per minute per IP address
 78	- Exponential backoff for rate-limited requests
 79	- Request queuing for high-volume operations
 80	
 81	## Server Management
 82	
 83	### Key Features
 84	
 85	- Server provisioning
 86	- Server status monitoring
 87	- Resource usage tracking
 88	- Server actions (start, stop, restart, etc.)
 89	- Console access
 90	
